In [ ]:
def Durbin_Watson_test(x):
    x_square_sum = np.vdot(x, x)
    print("x_square_sum = ", x_square_sum)
    size = x.size
    print("size = ", size)
    x_d = np.zeros((size))
    print("x_d = ", x_d)
    l_size = size - 1
    for i in range(l_size):
        x_d[i + 1] = x[i + 1] - x[i]
    print("x_d = ", x_d)
    d = np.vdot(x_d, x_d) / x_square_sum
    print("d = ", d)
    return(d)
